NAME: Teamwork
DESCRIPTION: Teamwork attribute defines your ability to work with other people to achieve a common goal

NAME: Initiative
DESCRIPTION: Initiative attribute defines your resourcefulness and ability to finish delegated tasks without any help

NAME: Consistency
DESCRIPTION: Consistency attribute is about your ability to be dependable, reliable and persistent in your actions and work habits

NAME: Diligence
DESCRIPTION: Diligence attribute is shown as alertness and dedication in continual effort to accomplish a task

NAME: Effort
DESCRIPTION: Effort attribute defines your ability to smoothly and adaptively carryout complex activities or job functions

NAME: Knowledge
DESCRIPTION: Knowledge attribute defines a level of your qualifications, required for for successful job performance

NAME: Persuasion
DESCRIPTION: Persuasion attribute defines your ability to influence others to achieve your goals

NAME: Empathy
DESCRIPTION: Empathy attribute defines your capacity to understand or feel what another person is experiencing from within

NAME: Endurance
DESCRIPTION: Endurance attribute shows your power to withstand challenging tasks and work conditions

NAME: Improvement
DESCRIPTION: Improvement attribute defines your ability to improve overall performance in any identified area of work

NAME: Grit
DESCRIPTION: Grit attribute defines your passion and perseverance toward a goal despite being confronted by significant obstacles and distractions

NAME: Perseverance
DESCRIPTION: Perseverance attribute defines your ability to generate continued effort to do or achieve something despite difficulties, failure, or opposition

NAME: Leadership
DESCRIPTION: Leadership attribute defines your ability to make sound decisions and inspire others to perform well

NAME: Curiosity
DESCRIPTION: Curiosity attribute shows your attitude towards getting new knowledge or information

NAME: Communication
DESCRIPTION: Communication attribute defines your ability to convey information to another effectively and efficiently

NAME: Flexibility
DESCRIPTION: Flexibility attribute defines your ability to adapt to new situations, improvise, and shift strategies to meet different types of challenges

NAME: Willingness to Learn
DESCRIPTION: Willingness to learn attribute defines your readiness to know new things and to improve yourself

NAME: Energy
DESCRIPTION: Energy attribute defines your ability to perform active actions and achieve personal goals

NAME: Cooperation
DESCRIPTION: Cooperation attribute shows your ability to work together with other people and achieve common goals

NAME: Enthusiasm
DESCRIPTION: Enthusiasm attribute defines your ability to show a keen interest in a subject or an work activity, as well as a readiness to get involved

NAME: Resilience
DESCRIPTION: Resilience attribute defines your ability to cope with and rise to the inevitable challenges, problems and set-backs you meet in the course of work
